Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:37.58,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}My Silky Love 24時間ずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.58,0:07:41.12,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}My Silky Love キミのこと想うたび
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.12,0:07:44.65,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}My Silky Love もどかしいこの気持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:48.66,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}My Silky Love ただ溢れかえってく
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.06,0:07:52.54,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}スキと言えば簡単なのに
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.62,0:07:55.92,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}キミが前に来ちゃうと
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.19,0:08:02.33,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}個性がそびえ　私のコトを邪魔してる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:06.73,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いつもならば強気でイケる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:10.24,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そんな性格なのに
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.43,0:08:16.41,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どんな頑張ってみても壁は崩せない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.52,0:08:20.14,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}察して欲しい…　この気持ちを
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:23.71,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}だから私は　いつもキミに
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.71,0:08:27.36,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}大好きだよと　送る視線
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:31.11,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}最大の勇気で！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.34,0:08:34.71,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}破れそうな　シルクノハート
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.81,0:08:38.35,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}キミに逢って気づいた　やっと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.35,0:08:44.00,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}愛には不器用だったんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.45,0:08:48.99,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}忘れかけた　恋の傷跡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:52.43,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}急に疼きだしたの　キュンと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:56.02,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いつかは私らしくスキと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.10,0:09:01.99,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}言わなきゃ…今より弱くなっちゃうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:37.58,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}My Silky Love　24小时中一直
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.58,0:07:41.12,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}My Silky Love　每当想起你的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.12,0:07:44.65,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}My Silky Love　心神不定的这份感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:48.66,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}My Silky Love　只是渐渐地漫溢出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.06,0:07:52.54,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明明说喜欢是如此简单
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.62,0:07:55.92,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}当你来到面前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.19,0:08:02.33,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}乖张的个性却总妨碍着我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:06.73,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}平常的话可以逞强下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:10.24,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明明是这种性格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.43,0:08:16.41,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}无论如何努力也无法打破壁障
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.52,0:08:20.14,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}希望你能觉察到 这份心情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:23.71,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所以我 总是向你送去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.71,0:08:27.36,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「最喜欢你了」的视线
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:31.11,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}用最大的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.34,0:08:34.71,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}似乎快要扯破 丝绒般的心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.81,0:08:38.35,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}遇到你才终于明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.35,0:08:44.00,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}原来爱是这样笨拙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.45,0:08:48.99,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}即将忘却 恋爱的伤痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:52.43,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}却突然再次隐隐作疼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:56.02,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}如果有一天不说出自己的喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.10,0:09:01.99,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}将会变得比现在更加懦弱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------正文------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.86,0:00:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高须同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.84,0:00:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.06,0:00:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去追她
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.65,0:00:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高须同学从左边  我从右边  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.67,0:00:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.76,0:00:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生会长  他们在走廊跑起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次就宽大处理了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.99,0:00:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追上了要说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.81,0:00:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.28,0:00:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.46,0:00:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.31,0:00:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在入口
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.97,0:00:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大河  听得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.19,0:00:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂大河  你一直都想知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.02,0:00:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…我也喜欢高须同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.51,0:00:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢高须龙儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.48,0:01:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢着  一直喜欢着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.45,0:01:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一直觉得必须把他让给你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.20,0:01:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好朋友的你需要高须同学什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.60,0:01:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是傲慢的我的误解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.79,0:01:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也小看了你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.70,0:01:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才也说过吧  我的幸福由我来决定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.75,0:01:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样的  你的幸福也只有你才能决定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…所以大河
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.22,0:01:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看你的做法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.58,0:01:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栉枝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.14,0:01:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚…刚才摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.52,0:01:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,止住了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.27,0:01:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓我一跳  还以为要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.87,0:01:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得我会哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.24,0:01:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般都会这样想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.13,0:02:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  这也是一种回报呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.67,0:02:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得吗  我说过我有能看得到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.67,0:02:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.41,0:02:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实呢  那是自己的…意气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.70,0:02:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意气？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.20,0:02:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说过我打棒球的弟弟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.67,0:02:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前我也打过棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.43,0:02:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说白了  还是我比较有才能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.53,0:02:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是却没能坚持下去  因为是女生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.60,0:02:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢  打算存了钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力考上体育大学  以全国级垒球为目标
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.15,0:02:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后啊  对着全世界呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我所选择并获得的幸福就是它了」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.73,0:02:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样的意气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.85,0:02:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栉枝…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是因为执着于这个  我决定不再哭泣了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.01,0:02:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算难过痛苦  也决定要努力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.18,0:03:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果有谁能看着我难过痛苦和哭泣也是回报吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.43,0:03:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个发夹怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.52,0:03:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.30,0:03:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个一定是要在平安夜送我作礼物的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.14,0:03:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  一开始真的不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.87,0:03:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为是大河送的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明决定不接受了  明明因此伤害了你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.64,0:03:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在高须同学面前戴着它  我想为此道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.72,0:03:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.39,0:03:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…现在在什么地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我房间里  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我不能收下那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.35,0:03:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢  还有一个能看到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.11,0:03:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高须同学喜欢大河
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.78,0:03:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:04:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  高须同学  我们就此再见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.85,0:04:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向着看得到的东西冲刺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.96,0:04:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.40,0:04:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊  高须
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.76,0:04:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高须Hey
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高须Hey  高须～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.98,0:04:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.29,0:04:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这人还算正直
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想就算逃了也一定会来打工
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.16,0:04:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…关于刚才的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.80,0:05:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到了小实的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.72,0:05:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.63,0:05:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要笑  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工结束了再听我说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果…如果我再想逃的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.35,0:05:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好抓住我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.57,0:05:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.99,0:05:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿到不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们说谎了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰…泰子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大河
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这种地方到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.68,0:06:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要碰我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.61,0:06:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闹别扭也该有个限度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.04,0:06:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人又能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  大河？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.92,0:06:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是高须同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.55,0:06:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你一直照顾她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.04,0:06:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子今后要和我一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁要和你这种人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.77,0:06:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你的男人  还有他的小鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.93,0:06:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.48,0:06:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.78,0:06:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白的是泰泰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.47,0:06:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定好禁止打工的  但是小龙你却说谎破坏了约定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.74,0:06:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事不能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.97,0:06:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么不能原谅…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.70,0:06:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为了我增加工作  所以才倒下了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以由我来工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.19,0:06:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这有什么不对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是家人  家人这样互相扶持是理所当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.19,0:06:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人的事我不管
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.90,0:06:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要我家的小龙努力学习
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:07:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到自己想做的事  出色地活下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.64,0:07:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有学习的是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做自己想做的事  没成为出色的人的不都是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.77,0:07:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…龙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.65,0:07:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把自己的失败推给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.19,0:07:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大河…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.40,0:07:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大河？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大河
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住  大河
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.57,0:09:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个混蛋老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事业失败就逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.16,0:09:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  然后就叫我亲生母亲来养我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.76,0:09:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  那个人已经有新的家庭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子里有了孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人个子很高  所以出生的孩子的腿一定也会很长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我像是个未进化的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.35,0:09:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的…这样的家庭我怎么融入得进去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在的话  家里就变得不自在了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个混蛋老爸那里也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.84,0:09:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有我在大家才会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…一直…这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.47,0:09:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.41,0:09:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰子一定会有更好的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.19,0:09:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又还年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是高中也还能重新读
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.93,0:10:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人都很任性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.28,0:10:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会根据自己的情况来连累他人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.37,0:10:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  也许正是我在连累泰子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.37,0:10:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我…还是个小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.64,0:10:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  如果没有我的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.54,0:10:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊  你这猪脑袋  不要轻生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像有个很大的误会…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.75,0:10:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秃子秃子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.20,0:10:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样做又能怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.27,0:10:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「都是因为我在」这种天真的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是也说了啊  刚才
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.21,0:10:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.65,0:10:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.05,0:10:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.75,0:10:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你喜欢谁  不管你今后会和谁一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.73,0:10:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.77,0:10:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想看着你…看着你高须龙儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:11:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…所以不要再说自己不在就好了这种话了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事  你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.39,0:11:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事个头啊  你想杀了我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌  真糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.68,0:11:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊  我不是说过道歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.82,0:11:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你没说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.37,0:11:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是会斤斤计较啊  啥血型的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.75,0:11:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是金牛座的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.39,0:11:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星座占卜啥的我不太懂  成吉思汗很好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.39,0:11:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}成吉思汗：这里指的是日本的一种羊肉料理，发源于北海道，\N在一种铁制的形状如帽子的特制锅上，将羊肉片和蔬菜蘸上调料汁，边烤边吃。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.49,0:11:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.61,0:11:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2个月后我就18岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.43,0:11:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样从泰子她们那里逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.49,0:11:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃啊逃啊  睡了醒了  再逃啊逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到我的生日  然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.54,0:11:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就嫁给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话我们也是大人了  不会让任何人妨碍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到死我的人生都给你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.67,0:11:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我…等等——！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.38,0:12:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狡猾  不是说好我先说给你听的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.63,0:12:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这只狡猾狗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊  这种事就该让男人说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我说  我和小实说好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要让她看看我的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那么…一起说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.34,0:12:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,0:12:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.84,0:12:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了  在这种重要的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.66,0:12:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无…无视掉  快点继续  又冷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.21,0:12:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么啊  那不是太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.86,0:12:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点接
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.98,0:12:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.88,0:12:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂高须  你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.88,0:12:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北村？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.85,0:13:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和逢坂的家人为了找你们到处联络
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  现在就到我说的地方来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.49,0:13:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等  北村
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.65,0:13:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头发上粘到了鼻涕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.64,0:13:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要在你家集合
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.08,0:13:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的母亲的包围网
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没来过我这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.33,0:13:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天阿姨她们也不在  快进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样会感冒的  先去淋浴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.26,0:13:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直走到底右转
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  这些也拿上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.43,0:13:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然让你来费心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.49,0:13:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.92,0:13:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.04,0:13:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大河  鞋子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.29,0:13:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川岛？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.41,0:13:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.41,0:13:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  高须同学的换洗衣服佑作会拿来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之真是麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.20,0:13:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.22,0:13:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊  喜欢大河吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.05,0:14:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…你说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.40,0:14:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.16,0:14:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.59,0:14:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.90,0:14:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.81,0:14:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢大河
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.80,0:14:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一脸傻样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.73,0:14:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你逼我说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大河
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.99,0:14:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我担心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.63,0:14:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙你这家伙你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.33,0:14:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小实小实  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.57,0:14:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大河  大河…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北村
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.13,0:14:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么多事麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里  比起这个今后你们打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.39,0:14:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.12,0:14:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算私奔GEN
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.24,0:14:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.43,0:14:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是认真的GEN
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.51,0:15:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.80,0:15:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  还剩两个月…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认同个什么劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私奔然后结婚？  这也太飞越了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要等龙儿18岁嘛  这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.41,0:15:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说了你们打算睡在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…那  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.34,0:15:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之商务旅馆或漫画咖啡厅之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.20,0:15:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算一直都持续那样的生活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.25,0:15:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  所以回来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.24,0:15:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还回得来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.21,0:15:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发出搜索的请求  传闻传到学校的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.43,0:15:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好会退学的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.57,0:15:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.82,0:15:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望的东西总是会坏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.14,0:15:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以决定什么都不再抱希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.21,0:15:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我的心意得到了回报
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的愿望实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.24,0:16:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想要打破这个「希望的东西总是会坏掉」的厄运
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  必须打破它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.47,0:16:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…所以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我贴身放了很久的存折
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.67,0:16:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工积攒的钱都存在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.21,0:16:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.52,0:16:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高须同学  大河
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.90,0:16:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点  完全都不觉得你们是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对无法赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.04,0:16:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小实…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.14,0:16:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  如果这就是你的做法的话我也不能反对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.37,0:16:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了终有一天把它还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.34,0:16:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  我家别墅的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.54,0:16:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去过一次的话应该知道在哪儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.01,0:16:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川岛…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.74,0:16:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我忘了怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.54,0:16:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个拿着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}米券
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.67,0:16:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么亚美  今天谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.07,0:17:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小实我和亚美还有些悄悄话要说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.87,0:17:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要和你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.22,0:17:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们和好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢  笨蛋吉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.81,0:17:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了快走吧  这家伙也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.19,0:17:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  小实  笨蛋吉  再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定还会再见的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.67,0:17:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.80,0:17:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.88,0:17:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.83,0:17:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说回来放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腰软了已经站不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.72,0:17:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  你在做什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  要给我看你的哭脸么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.31,0:17:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼泪可是心灵的鼻血啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是为了什么的而流眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.44,0:17:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为大河被高须同学抢走了？  还是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.94,0:17:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.46,0:18:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再哭泣…明明已经决定了绝对不再哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.92,0:18:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难为情的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.49,0:18:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  也明白了一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.54,0:18:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走廊上跌倒会流鼻血
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.33,0:18:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生中跌倒会流眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.47,0:18:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋吗  我们要谈人生还早着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后  十年后  二十年后  六十年后都会继续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了一定要逃出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.59,0:18:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰泰的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.35,0:18:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心  会成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.82,0:18:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.20,0:18:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…对了  把干燥机带出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.78,0:18:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想只有我的行李很多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.17,0:18:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么别拿些轻飘飘的衣服来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.07,0:18:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会增加体积
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.26,0:18:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.27,0:18:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备完了马上出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事的话马上打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.56,0:19:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  立刻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.12,0:19:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.15,0:19:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹦…小鹦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.76,0:19:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.17,0:19:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给小龙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.87,0:19:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去外公和外婆的家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给他们看了这个手表就会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}一直以来谢谢你的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.68,0:19:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  魅罗乃？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.63,0:19:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傍晚时来联络说是暂时要休息
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.78,0:19:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.94,0:19:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有多小孩子气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.25,0:20:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃跑的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.23,0:20:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算过了生日…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.16,0:20:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是不会长大的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.66,0:20:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chocolate
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天不是刚炫耀过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.23,0:20:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点吃掉吧  打算让人看到什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.48,0:20:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到保质期快过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.39,0:20:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说学校不是交换巧克力的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.63,0:20:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有交换啊  我只是拿来而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.22,0:20:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧大河…咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.11,0:20:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请假了  高须同学也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.82,0:20:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  两个人一起感冒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发烧了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.32,0:20:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油加油加油加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:20:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大桥加油加油加油…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.63,0:20:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.12,0:21:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不去送行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算内心再坚强的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.97,0:21:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被大河和高须同学一起甩了也不行了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.45,0:21:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要和你打雪仗…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.89,0:21:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招  纯洁的白球
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.95,0:21:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是私奔用的食物  就选了些比较大人味的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.20,0:21:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  雪茄巧克力和鸡味仙贝  还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.18,0:21:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也做了便当哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.44,0:21:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.34,0:21:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私奔的便当不应该是车站的便当吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.40,0:21:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.15,0:21:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妈妈…怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.62,0:21:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人会在意也只是因为面子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.13,0:22:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不会惹出大骚乱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.16,0:22:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  泰泰怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.83,0:22:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.00,0:22:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是现在我能说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.01,0:22:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰泰说我们三个人是家人的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.58,0:22:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心里真是高兴得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的家庭又是那个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.05,0:22:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就想这样成为真的家人的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.02,0:22:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰泰  会哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.69,0:22:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.94,0:22:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是永别  所以说不是讨厌私奔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.06,0:22:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也觉得那样非常不错  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.59,0:22:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.81,0:22:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…大河
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.49,0:22:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子他爸…他他他他他他他爸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.72,0:22:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个的确是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.57,0:22:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.78,0:23:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面  我是你们的外孙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.65,0:23:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高须龙儿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.49,0:23:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  这家伙是我的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.84,0:23:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  有个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.63,0:23:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是逃避  我们要…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.39,0:23:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙儿让我看到的  只属于龙儿的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.77,0:23:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次该轮到我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.98,0:23:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.17,0:23:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要笑哦  不要生气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.18,0:21:16.80,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}似てても違うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.61,0:21:20.31,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}マンダリン　オレンジ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.08,0:21:23.66,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}友達　恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.40,0:21:27.56,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}２人のココロも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:30.53,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}傷つきたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.33,0:21:33.95,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}私は逃げてた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.75,0:21:37.30,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そしたら光も
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.11,0:21:41.35,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}射してはくれない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.74,0:21:44.24,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}奇跡なのにね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.10,0:21:47.68,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}出逢いも恋も
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.55,0:21:50.94,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}種もつぼみも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.02,0:21:58.74,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}まだ青い　実でさえも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.80,0:22:01.94,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}オレンジ色は　あの日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.94,0:22:03.48,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}見た夕焼けを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.48,0:22:06.77,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}思い出させてくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.92,0:22:08.81,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}２つの影が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.81,0:22:13.71,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}手を繋いでるみたいだった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.79,0:22:15.72,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}オレンジ　いつか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.72,0:22:17.25,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}甘くなるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.25,0:22:20.52,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}それともしぼんじゃうの？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.59,0:22:23.98,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}私の未来知りたくなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.98,0:22:26.53,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ぜんぶ食べた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.53,0:22:29.80,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}すっぱい…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.86,0:22:38.26,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好きだけど泣けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.74,0:22:44.74,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}オレンジ色に　早く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.74,0:22:46.35,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}なりたい果実
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.35,0:22:49.64,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}キミの光を浴びて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.75,0:22:53.15,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}理想や夢は膨らむばかり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.15,0:22:56.43,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}気づいてよ　ねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.62,0:22:58.60,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}オレンジ　今日も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.60,0:23:00.03,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}食べてみたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.03,0:23:03.37,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}まだすっぱくて　泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.52,0:23:06.92,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}私みたいで残せないから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.92,0:23:12.73,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ぜんぶ食べた　好きだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.92,0:23:16.19,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}すっぱい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.26,0:23:22.82,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泣けるよ　好きだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.14,0:23:24.51,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好きだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.18,0:21:16.80,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}虽然相似却并不相同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.61,0:21:20.31,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Mandarin  orange
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.08,0:21:23.66,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}朋友  恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.40,0:21:27.56,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}2颗悸动的心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:30.53,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}因为不想伤害你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.33,0:21:33.95,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所以我逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.75,0:21:37.30,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}于是就连阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.11,0:21:41.35,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}也再也无法照进来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.74,0:21:44.24,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明明就是奇迹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.10,0:21:47.68,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}邂逅也是恋爱也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.55,0:21:50.94,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}种子也是花蕾也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.02,0:21:58.74,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就连仍然青涩的果实也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.80,0:22:06.77,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}橙色  让我想起了那天的夕阳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.92,0:22:08.81,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}两个人的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.81,0:22:13.71,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就好像牵着手一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.79,0:22:15.72,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}橙子  何时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.72,0:22:17.25,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}才能变得甘甜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.25,0:22:20.52,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}还是会枯萎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.59,0:22:23.98,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我想要知道我的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.98,0:22:26.53,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}才全部全部吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.53,0:22:29.80,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好酸…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.86,0:22:38.26,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}虽然喜欢你  却会哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.74,0:22:46.35,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}想要早些成为橙色的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.35,0:22:49.64,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}沐浴着你的阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.75,0:22:53.15,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}理想和梦想不断膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.15,0:22:56.43,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}快察觉到吧  呐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.62,0:23:00.03,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今天也品尝了橙子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.03,0:23:03.37,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}依然酸涩  不禁落泪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.52,0:23:06.92,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不能让它像我一样被丢弃
